OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774515911
OL,3,CGarnacho fined for speeding away from
OL,4,CMan United training ground
OL,6,FPremier League footballer Alejandro
OL,7,FGarnacho has been convicted of
OL,8,Fspeeding away from Manchester United's
OL,9,Ftraining ground just days before he
OL,10,Fleft the club.
OL,12,FThe 21-year-old winger was behind the
OL,13,Fwheel of his black Audi RS 3 when he
OL,14,Ftriggered a speed camera close to the
OL,15,Fclub's Carrington facility.
OL,17,FThe incident, when Garnacho was
OL,18,Fdriving at 50mph in a 40mph zone,
OL,19,Fhappened on 26 August 2025, four days
OL,20,Fbefore he signed for Chelsea in a #40
OL,21,Fmillion deal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
