OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774515911
OL,3,CGarnacho fined for speeding away from
OL,4,CMan United training ground
OL,6,FThrough lawyers, Garnacho pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to speeding at Liverpool
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court, and issued an
OL,9,Fapology saying he is "embarrassed" by
OL,10,Fthe incident.
OL,12,F"Mr Garnacho accepts that he committed
OL,13,Fthe offence of exceeding the speed
OL,14,Flimit and has pleaded guilty to the
OL,15,Foffence," his lawyers at JMW
OL,16,FSolicitors wrote.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@bO]tD@AOUwD@IO]
