PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774515911
OL,3,CGarnacho fined for speeding away from
OL,4,CMan United training ground
OL,6,F"Mr Garnacho explains this was an
OL,7,Foversight on his part and apologises
OL,8,Ffor the offence. Our Client is
OL,9,Fembarrassed that he is currently in
OL,10,Fthis position and apologises to the
OL,11,FCourt for the excess speed offence."
OL,13,FGarnacho was also charged with failing
OL,14,Fto respond to a Greater Manchester
OL,15,FPolice letter about the speeding
OL,16,Foffence, when he was asked to identify
OL,17,Fthe driver of his car in October last
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@dO]
