PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774515911
OL,3,CGarnacho fined for speeding away from
OL,4,CMan United training ground
OL,6,FHowever that offence was withdrawn
OL,7,Fafter Garnacho pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fspeeding.
OL,10,FMagistrate Jane Haynes sentenced the
OL,11,Ffootballer to a #660 fine, with an
OL,12,Forder to pay #120 in costs and a #264
OL,13,Fvictim surcharge. Garnacho was also
OL,14,Fissued with three penalty points on
OL,15,Fhis licence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
