CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774515911
OL,3,CGarnacho fined for speeding away from
OL,4,CMan United training ground
OL,6,FThe Argentine international came
OL,7,Fthrough the Manchester United academy,
OL,8,Fbut left the club after falling out of
OL,9,Ffavour under former boss Ruben Amorim.
OL,10,FHe made 36 appearances for the team
OL,11,Fbefore joining Chelsea.
OL,13,FGarnacho was convicted and sentenced
OL,14,Fin a hearing conducted behind closed
OL,15,Fdoors under the Single Justice
OL,16,FProcedure.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
